        <body>       
                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>Mount Tabor Oregon<lb/>
                July 7 &#39;90<lb/></p>
            <p>Dr Sabato Morais<lb/>
                Minister <sic>Portugese</sic> Congregation<lb/> 
                Mickv&#233; Israel<lb/>
                Philadelphia<lb/>
                Pa<lb/></p>
            <p>My Dear Sir&#58;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>I have been<lb/> carrying on&#44; of late&#44; a most interesting<lb/> correspondence with your learned<lb/> and eloquent friend&#44; Mr. D. Solis Cohen<lb/> of the city of Portland Oregon&#44;<lb/> The place at which I write is a suburb<lb/> of said city.<lb/></p>
            <p>The subject of our correspondence<lb/> has been the present faith &#38;<lb/> practice of the Jewish people.<lb/>  I am a Baptist minister&#44; deeply<lb/> interested in the <hi rend="underline">Hope of Israel</hi>.<lb/>  Mr. Cohen has very kindly and<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>clearly answered many of my<lb/> questions&#44; but has suggested that<lb/> I make inquiry of you touching<lb/> may of the most important<lb/> topics.  He has assured me that<lb/> you would take pleasure in<lb/> answering my questions when<lb/> I assure you it is in no<lb/> controversial spirit that they are<lb/> asked.  My only desire is to<lb/> learn of prevailing faith among<lb/> the Jewish people of today.<lb/>  I would therefore very respectfully<lb/> ask the following questions&#58;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>1<hi rend="sup">st</hi>. <hi rend="underline">Do the Jewish people generally&#44; today&#44;<lb/> believe in Messiah at all</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>2<hi rend="sup">nd</hi>. <hi rend="underline">Do they believe that the Millenium<lb/> or age of perfect peace or tranquility<lb/> will dawn before or after the<lb/> coming of Messiah</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi>. <hi rend="underline">Do you believe the Messiah will be<lb/> a Prince of Peace who will<lb/> reign with the ceptre of universal</hi><lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="3"/>
            <p><hi rend="underline">empire&#44; on this earth&#44; or that&#44;<lb/> in other words&#44; all nations<lb/> will acknowledge the sovereignty<lb/> and sway</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>4<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. <hi rend="underline">o you believe&#44; in the <sic>resoration</sic><lb/> of the Jewish nation to<lb/> the Holy Land</hi>D&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>5<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. <hi rend="underline">Do you believe Jerusalem<lb/> will finally be restored to<lb/> her former glory</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>6<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. <hi rend="underline">If so&#44; how will such restoration<lb/> be brought about</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>It is said there are more Jews<lb/> in Jerusalem at the present<lb/> time than for many years.<lb/></p>
            <p>7<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. <hi rend="underline">If so&#44; what significance&#44; if<lb/> any has this fact</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>8<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. <hi rend="underline">So far as you know&#44; is there<lb/> any truth in the common<lb/> report that the Rothchilds<lb/> and other wealthy Israelites<lb/> hold a mortgage on the<lb/> Holy Land as security<lb/> for loans made the Turkish</hi><lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="4"/>
            <p><hi rend="underline">Government</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>9<hi rend="sup">th</hi> <hi rend="underline">Under any circumstances<lb/> do you believe the Jews<lb/> will ever again become<lb/> a distinct nation under<lb/> a separate government<lb/> of their own</hi>&#63;<lb/></p>
            <p>These questions cover the topics<lb/> I am most deeply <sic>inerested</sic><lb/> in at the present time.<lb/></p>
            <p>Answers to these from so learned<lb/> a man as yourself will be<lb/> very gratefully received.<lb/>  Hoping this may not be too<lb/> great an inflection upon you&#44;<lb/> I remain my dear sir<lb/> Very Respectfully &#38; Cordially&#44;<lb/> Cephas C. Bateman<lb/> Pastor Baptist Church<lb/> Mt Tabor. Oregon<lb/> Near Portland<lb/></p>
            
            <pb n="5"/>
            <p>Dr Sabato Morais<lb/>
                Minister <sic>Portugese</sic> Congregation<lb/>
                Mickv&#233; Israel<lb/>
                Philadelphia<lb/>
                Pa<lb/></p>
            
            <p>From<lb/> Rev. C. C. Bateman<lb/> Pastor Baptist Church<lb/> Mt Tabor<lb/> <hi rend="underline">Oregon</hi><lb/></p>
            </body>
